Extract PNG frames from HAFB FLIR video clip at frame rate of r=1 fps.
Output PNG filenames are of form CreditUnion_May25_flight1_NNNN.png :

ffmpeg -i clip3.mov -r 1 -f image2 CreditUnion_May25_flight1_%04d.png

=======================================================================

Extract jpg frames from input.mp4 at a frame rate of r=1 fps.  Output jpg
filenames are of form foo-001.jpg, foo-002.jpg, etc.  They have pixel sizes
W x H:

ffmpeg -i input.mp4 -r 1 -s W x H -f image2 foo-%03d.jpg

ffmpeg -i fullpath/input.mp4 -r 1  -f image2 output_fullpath/foo-%03d.jpg



